2006-06-13  Marius Vollmer  <marius.vollmer@nokia.com>

	Released 2.3
	
	* maemo-mini-curl.c (ssl_app_verify_callback): Make certificate
	file readable for everyone.
	(fetch): Unlink destination file when libcurl returns an error.

2006-06-01  Marius Vollmer  <marius.vollmer@nokia.com>

	* Makefile.am (bin_PROGRAMS): Added maemo-mini-curl-cert-gui.
	* maemo-cert-gui.c: New.
	
	* configure.ac (MINICURL): Remove dependency on cst.
	(CERTGUI): New.

	* maemo-mini-curl.c (fetch): Output newline after error message
	from libcurl.
	(ssl_app_verify_callback): Do not do verification here.  Execute
	maemo-mini-curl-cert-gui to do it.
	(main): Do not call g_type_init, it is no longer needed and we
	don't link with libcst and glib anymore.
	
2006-05-12  Marius Vollmer  <marius.vollmer@nokia.com>

	* debian/rules (config.status): Do not depend on configure, but
	call autogen.sh when configure does not exist.

2006-05-04  Marius Vollmer  <marius.vollmer@nokia.com>

	Released 2.1
	
	* maemo-mini-curl.c: New.
	* https.cc: Moved libcurl related code to maemo-mini-curl to avoid
	linking libapt-pkg and OpenSSL into the same program.
	* Makefile.am, configure.ac: Adapted accordingly.
	
2006-05-02  Marius Vollmer  <marius.vollmer@nokia.com>

	* Makefile.am (deb): Added target for making nice debs.
	(EXTRA_DIST): Distribute make-package.

2006-04-26  Marius Vollmer  <marius.vollmer@nokia.com>

	* Started.

